            {
               "text": "### Images from Athens\n\nThese images are copyright for Athens and allowed to be used according to the license determined by them.\n\nTo visualize all images, use the left and right arrows on the slide below.",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p><div class=\"htSlides\"><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">1 / 3</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgAthens\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgAthens', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Erechtheion temples in Athens, Greece (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('38444844-0e52-4748-89f7-025ebd713e10'); return false;\"><i>The Acropolis Museum, 02/01/2025</i></a>). Photo taken on <htdate0>, during a visit to the site.</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">2 / 3</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"img5\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img5', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Columns present at the Parthenon, Greece. Photo taken on <htdate0>, during a visit to the archaeological site.</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">3 / 3</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"img0\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img0', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Map of the \"world\" © Trustees of the British Museum (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('5e23a3eb-7323-44ab-b9e1-88acfd1e21a6'); return false;\"><i>The British Museum, 12/30/2024</i></a>). Shared under the <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/\" target=\"_blank\">Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0)</a>.</div></div><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-left htSlidePrev\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(-1);\"></i><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right htSlideNext\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(1);\"></i></div></p>",
