            },
            {
               "text": "### Image Descriptions\n- **Slide 1 / 3**: Erechtheion temples in Athens, Greece (*The Acropolis Museum, 02/01/2025*). Photo taken on <htdate0>, during a visit to the site.\n- **Slide 2 / 3**: Columns present at the Parthenon, Greece. Photo taken on <htdate0>, during a visit to the archaeological site.\n- **Slide 3 / 3**: Map of the \"world\" © Trustees of the British Museum (*The British Museum, 12/30/2024*). Shared under the Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0).",
